data.description: Escape to your secluded sanctuary encompassing 8.5 acres, complete with an idyllic wooded area ideal for hunting and exploration. This picturesque ranch-style abode boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, and the highly sought-after split floor plan layout. Step into the main living room, where vaulted ceilings and skylights infuse the space with an airy, inviting atmosphere. Adjacent, an additional family room offers generous space for gatherings, seamlessly extending from the main living area. Entertain with ease in the open concept kitchen and dining area, featuring convenient bar seating and direct access to the rear deck, perfect for those summer barbecues. Retreat to the master suite, offering both an en-suite bathroom and a spacious walk-in closet for ultimate comfort and convenience. Two additional bedrooms and another full bath round out the well-designed layout of this home. Outside, a substantial 50x30 pole barn awaits, boasting concrete floors and ample lighting! Call to schedule!
